issue.title: Look into actual login functionality
issue.body:
If we want to actually be able to have login functionality via a selfie, we will need to look into the logistics of doing so. Currently nothing at all is being done with the validate functionality. 

At the very least we should only enter the new user in the database if they do not match any of the existing photos. Currently we are just logging yay or nay and moving on.
